    "description": "A new kind of smash-and-grab battle!<br />\r\nEnjoy the realistic behavior of objects and accidental 3D action!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n--- Three mini-games to play by smashing objects ---<br />\r\nSurvival Stage: Fight off zombies that attack one after another.<br />\r\nA target shooting stage: Hit boxes flowing on a conveyor belt.<br />\r\nThe Boss Challenge Stage: You face off against powerful monsters in single combat.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n--- Two styles of play that connect you with other players ---<br />\r\nIn single-player mode: Perform well in each mini-game in order to move up the online ranking.<br />\r\nIn Multiplayer: You can fight and cooperate with other players online!*<br />\r\n* Please consider this as a bonus, as synchronization may be out of sync due to differences in computer performance.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n--- Immediately dive into an exciting play space ---<br />\r\nThe game is named &quot;Casual&quot;, so you can choose a character and start playing right away!<br />\r\nThe action is intuitive, with buttons assigned to each hand and foot! The characters are like your alter ego!<br />\r\nThe exhilaration of smashing huge objects is addictive!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n--- Credits and materials provided by ---<br />\r\nThe very cute Unitychan (© UTJ/UCL) will be participating in the game.<br />\r\nSome of the sounds are by &quot;YouFulca&quot;.",
